---
title: Rigatoni & Spinach Marinara 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: This pasta dish is as comforting and satisfying as it is quick and simple to make. You’ll simmer fresh rigatoni in a tangy, garlicky marinara sauce, then add fresh spinach that wilts in perfectly. Finish with a dollop of creamy ricotta cheese and a sprinkle of chili flakes, and serve with buttery ciabatta toast for dunking.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6785685eaac2798c14863880-8205c212.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6785685eaac2798c14863880-en-US.pdf
time required: 15 minutes
cuisine: Southern Europe
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/rigatoni-and-spinach-marinara-6785685eaac2798c14863880
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 730 kcal
  fat: 24 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
